## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not capture the full diversity of funeral practices across different cultures and regions. Additionally, the data is limited to trends observed up to 2023, and ongoing developments in the funeral industry may not be fully represented. Further research could include interviews with funeral directors and surveys of younger individuals to gain deeper insights into evolving preferences.